", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>in <code>SensorManager::SensorContainer::RunLoop()</code></p>\n<p>When calculating sleep time:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"c1\">// Calculate an appropriate sleep time.</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">maxUpdateRate</span> <span class=\"o\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">sleepTime</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mf\">1.0</span> <span class=\"o\">/</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">maxUpdateRate</span><span class=\"p\">));</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">else</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">sleepTime</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">1e6</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>if no update rate is specified then <code>maxUpdateRate</code> evaluates to <code>GZ_DBL_MIN</code> which results in <code>1.0/GZ_DBL_MIN</code> sleep time</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-03-05T04:37:11.471321+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:45:22.590014+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 555}